  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparision of two different cannulation techniques on the neurological outcome in cardiac
      surcical procedures. Study hypothesis: Cannulation of the axilaris artery can reduce
      neurolocical side effects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
